Akkineni Nagarjuna Rao, known mononymously as Nagarjuna, is an Indian actor, film producer, television presenter, and entrepreneur. Nagarjuna has acted in over 100 films, predominantly in Telugu, along with a few Hindi and Tamil language films. Wikipedia
Born: 29 August 1959 (age 62 years), Chennai
Height: 1.78 m
Spouse: Amala Akkineni (m. 1992), Lakshmi Daggubati (m. 1984–1990)
Upcoming movie: Brahmāstra
Children: Naga Chaitanya, Akhil Akkineni
